Special case: triangle

For n=3:

R_{PC}(3)=\sqrt{\frac{\pi}{3\tan(\pi/3)}}
=
\sqrt{\frac{\pi}{3\sqrt{3}}}

R_{PS}(3)=2\sqrt{\frac{1}{3\sqrt{3}}}

and still

R_{CS}(3)=\frac{2}{\sqrt{\pi}}

which matches what we found before.

